@SecurityCore.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5136

### Create incident
POST {{SecurityCore.Api_HostAddress}}/api/incidents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Suspicious login attempt",
  "description": "Multiple failed login attempts detected on the admin account.",
  "severity": 2,
  "assetName": "Admin Portal",
  "createdBy": "melih"
}

### Get incidents
GET {{SecurityCore.Api_HostAddress}}/api/incidents?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### Add incident note
# Paste the incident id from the create response into the URL.
POST {{SecurityCore.Api_HostAddress}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "author": "melih",
  "message": "Initial triage completed. Keeping the incident under observation."
}

### Get incident notes
GET {{SecurityCore.Api_HostAddress}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/notes
Accept: application/json

###
